### Newsletter & Contact Forms — Exemplos HTTP

# Configure estas variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@adminToken = Bearer seu_jwt_token_aqui

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NEWSLETTER — Public Endpoints
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Subscribe to Newsletter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "metadata": {
    "name": "João Silva",
    "source": "homepage",
    "interests": ["eventos", "materiais"]
  }
}

### Subscribe - Duplicate (deve falhar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com"
}

### Unsubscribe from Newsletter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/unsubscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com"
}

### Check Newsletter Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/status/joao@example.com

### Check Status - Email Não Inscrito
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/status/nao-inscrito@example.com

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NEWSLETTER — Admin Endpoints
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List All Subscribers (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/subscribers?page=1&limit=50
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### List Subscribed Only (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/subscribers?page=1&limit=50&status=subscribed
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### List Unsubscribed (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/subscribers?page=1&limit=50&status=unsubscribed
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Export Subscribers to CSV (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/export
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Export Only Subscribed (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/export?status=subscribed
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Send Newsletter to All Subscribers (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
  "subject": "🎵 Novos eventos na comunidade - Junho 2026",
  "htmlContent": "<h2>Olá Community!</h2><p>Este mês temos eventos incríveis para você:</p><ul><li>Workshop de Harmonização</li><li>Roda de Conversa com Profissionais</li></ul><p>Acesse a plataforma para mais detalhes.</p>",
  "textContent": "Olá Community!\n\nEste mês temos eventos incríveis:\n- Workshop de Harmonização\n- Roda de Conversa com Profissionais\n\nAcesse a plataforma para mais detalhes."
}

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CONTACT FORMS — Public Endpoints
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Submit Contact Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Santos",
  "email": "maria@example.com",
  "phone": "(11) 98765-4321",
  "subject": "Dúvida sobre membership profissional",
  "message": "Olá! Gostaria de saber mais sobre como funciona a membership profissional. Qual é o custo mensal? Posso cancelar a qualquer momento? Quais benefícios incluem?"
}

### Submit Contact - Minimal
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pedro",
  "email": "pedro@example.com",
  "subject": "Feedback sobre a plataforma",
  "message": "A plataforma está excelente! Gostaria de sugerir um novo recurso."
}

### Submit Contact - With Phone
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Costa",
  "email": "ana@example.com",
  "phone": "11987654321",
  "subject": "Agendamento de sessão",
  "message": "Gostaria de agendar uma sessão de 50 minutos com um dos profissionais da plataforma. Qual é o procedimento?"
}

### Get Contact Message (Public - anyone with ID can view)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages/UUID_DA_MENSAGEM

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CONTACT FORMS — Admin Endpoints
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List All Messages (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/messages?page=1&limit=50
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### List New Messages Only (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/messages?page=1&limit=50&status=new
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### List Responded Messages (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/messages?page=1&limit=50&status=responded
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Search Messages (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/messages?page=1&limit=50&search=membership
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Update Message Status to Responded (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/messages/UUID_DA_MENSAGEM/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "responded"
}

### Update Message Status to Resolved (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/messages/UUID_DA_MENSAGEM/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "resolved"
}

### Mark as Spam (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/messages/UUID_DA_MENSAGEM/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "spam"
}

### Respond to Contact Message (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/messages/UUID_DA_MENSAGEM/reply
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
  "adminReply": "Olá Maria!\n\nObrigado por entrar em contato. Vou responder suas dúvidas:\n\n1. Custo: R$ 99/mês com todas as funcionalidades\n2. Cancelamento: Você pode cancelar a qualquer momento sem multas\n3. Benefícios: Acesso a todos os eventos, materiais, fórum e mais\n\nSe precisar de mais informações, estou à disposição!\n\nAbraços,\nEquipe Espalhe Melodias"
}

### Export Messages to CSV (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/export
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Export Only New Messages (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/export?status=new
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Get Message Stats (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/admin/stats
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VALIDAÇÃO DE ERROS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Invalid Email Format
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

### Contact Message Too Short
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "subject": "Oi",
  "message": "Msg curta"
}

### Contact Message Too Long (5000+ chars)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "subject": "Teste",
  "message": "Lorem ipsum... (mais de 5000 caracteres)"
}

### Spam Detection - Multiple URLs
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Spammer",
  "email": "spam@example.com",
  "subject": "Ganhe dinheiro rápido",
  "message": "Visite https://site1.com e https://site2.com e https://site3.com e https://site4.com para mais informações sobre como ganhar bitcoin!"
}

### Invalid Phone Format
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "phone": "123",
  "subject": "Dúvida",
  "message": "Gostaria de mais informações sobre seus serviços e como posso participar."
}

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# RATE LIMITING (Testar depois de enviar 1 subscribe + 3 contacts no mesmo IP)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Rate Limited - 4º Contact Message (será rejeitado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste",
  "email": "teste@example.com",
  "subject": "Teste",
  "message": "Esta é a quarta mensagem no mesmo dia, deve ser rejeitada"
}
